  "detailed_description": "World-building RPG \"Minable & Create\" is an easy-to-understand 2D screen sandbox game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619970/extras/47e6fe72507d37077a88a166aa12f7eb.poster.avif?t=1648134671\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619970/extras/47e6fe72507d37077a88a166aa12f7eb.webm?t=1648134671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619970/extras/47e6fe72507d37077a88a166aa12f7eb.mp4?t=1648134671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>● Can be dug</strong><br>Basically, anything in this world can be dug, destroyed, and materials (wood, stone, leather, ore) can be obtained.<br>You can dig terrain such as the sea and rocks, and create geoglyphs using the ground as a canvas.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619970/extras/47e6fe72507d37077a88a166aa12f7eb.poster.avif?t=1648134671\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619970/extras/47e6fe72507d37077a88a166aa12f7eb.webm?t=1648134671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619970/extras/47e6fe72507d37077a88a166aa12f7eb.mp4?t=1648134671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>● Can be created</strong><br>The collected materials can be processed to create items, tools, weapons and armor.<br>Create your own village or town where you can place the found NPCs as friends!<br>If you raise the player's Lv, you can make items at high speed.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619970/extras/e546bf7d1740ead99fee311c1e5a8680.poster.avif?t=1648134671\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619970/extras/e546bf7d1740ead99fee311c1e5a8680.webm?t=1648134671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619970/extras/e546bf7d1740ead99fee311c1e5a8680.mp4?t=1648134671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>● Can be connected</strong><br>You can \"publish\" the world you created.<br>Please try to attract many people to your world.<br>You can enjoy it even more by playing and connecting with everyone.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619970/extras/492af9c84041330d91619c468f9cb520.avif?t=1648134671\" width=616 height=252 /></span><br><br>See below for detailed operation methods and tips for beginners<br><strong> ● Game help page </strong><br><br>* You can check it by pressing the \"F1 key\" even in the game.<br><br><strong> ● Official page </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619970/extras/67c17fa5fa21bbbb5daabd6317d150cf.avif?t=1648134671\" width=616 height=252 /></span><br><br>Graphic material cooperation: (C) REFMAP, (C) finalbossblues<br>Copyright ©2021 TODOWORKS,TechnoPixel Inc. All Rights Reserved.",
